      "slowAudioRef": "dummy_slow_audio.mp3",
      "commonMispronunciation": "Saying 'kar-va-na'. While 'v' is accepted, 'w' (rounded lips) is much more standard for the 'waa' causative infix."
    },
    {
      "itemId": "p_4",
      "targetText": "सीखना",
